  missionTitle: 'Desh Ka Badlav: Das Saal Ka Hisaab'
  completionTitle: CHAPTER 23 COMPLETE
  completionMessage: Ten-year national development review passed. Health, learning,
    safety-justice and livelihood outcomes next global-cooperation chapter ko unlock
    karte hain.
  chapterNumber: 23
  nextChapterScene: 
  introTitle: CHAPTER 23 / DESH KA BADLAV
  introMessage: 'Das saal ke baad sawal speech ka nahi, evidence ka hai: sehat, padhai,
    nyay aur rozgaar aam zindagi mein kitna badla?'
  objectives:
  - {fileID: 1821760982}
  - {fileID: 2120252495}
  - {fileID: 1710715327}
  - {fileID: 141983484}
  - {fileID: 1128629875}
  - {fileID: 1097589847}
  - {fileID: 1678201598}
  - {fileID: 1658504937}
  - {fileID: 1520109128}
  - {fileID: 1230236485}
  - {fileID: 287923923}
  - {fileID: 211835124}
  objectiveLabels:
  - Baselines, missing data, privacy aur correction history audit karein
  - Primary care, maternal safety, medicines, referrals aur complaints review karein
  - Learning outcomes, adult literacy, teachers, libraries aur access audit karein
  - Prevention, forensics, survivor support, legal aid aur due process verify karein
  - Skills, apprenticeships, enterprises, payments aur worker safety review karein
  - Evidence-led phased reform ya mega target sprint mein decision lein
  - Need formula, state flexibility, audits, reserves aur opt-out compact renew karein
  - Tenders, ownership, samples, appeals aur whistleblower referrals publish karein
  - Energy, heat, flood, rivers, farm water aur shelters ka outcome audit karein
  - Household cost, forms, access, grievances aur media questions publish karein
  - Local response, evidence, witnesses, complaints aur weak districts report karein
  - Independent health, learning, justice and livelihood review dekhein
  milestoneSteps: 05000000080000000b000000
  milestoneTitles:
  - FOUR BASELINES VERIFIED
  - FEDERAL DELIVERY LOCKED
  - PUBLIC REVIEW READY
  milestoneMessages:
  - Baselines and four development pillars verified hain. Long-term reform model
    next hai.
  - Strategy, federal finance and procurement integrity locked hain. Resilience and
    public review next hain.
  - Resilience, citizen review and field safety audit complete hain. Independent
    ten-year review unlocked.
